CLASS 2 ASSIGNMENT Saturday 2 to 5 
 Chain of Thought (CoT) Prompting
In this technique, the AI is asked to show its thinking process step by step.
 That means the AI doesn‚Äôt just give an answer ‚Äî it also explains its reasoningLet‚Äôs solve this step by step This tells the AI to write out its reasoning process clearly.
Tree of Thoughts (ToT) Prompting
In this method, the AI doesn‚Äôt think in one straight line ‚Äî it tries multiple options (branches).
 Each branch represents a different possible answer, and the AI chooses the best one after comparing them.
 This approach works best for creative thinking or complex decision-making.
.
