FeatureChain of Thought (CoT)Tree of Thoughts (ToT)Thinking StyleStep-by-step reasoningBranch-based reasoningOutput TypeOne single reasoning pathMultiple reasoning pathsUse CaseLogical or math-based tasksCreative or complex tasksExampleSolving a math problemWriting a story or making a plan
üíº Real-World Examples
CoT Prompting: AI solving a math equation step by step.
ToT Prompting: AI generating several marketing strategies and choosing the best one.
